text: 🚨 Women's Health 2.0: The AI Era 🚨💬 Charting the evolution of women's healthcare in the AI era 💭🔍 Illuminating the promise and challenges of predictive tech to close the health gender gap 💻👩‍⚕️ Historically, women's health has been narrowly defined as reproductive health 🎉💪 It's time to recognize the unique biological and medical complexities of women's health 💪🔜 Join us in shaping a future where women's health is prioritized and understood 🌟#WomensHealth
